Package: r3js
Type: Package
Title: 'WebGL'-Based 3D Plotting using the 'three.js' Library
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Date: 2023-03-21
Author: Sam Wilks
Maintainer: Sam Wilks <sw463@cam.ac.uk>
Description: Provides R and 'JavaScript' functions to allow 'WebGL'-based 3D plotting
    using the 'three.js' 'JavaScript' library. Interactivity through roll-over 
    highlighting and toggle buttons is also supported.
License: AGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
